        <updateDate>2024-05-20T14:16:03Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[<p><strong>Stop Subsidizing&nbsp;Giant Mergers Act&nbsp;</strong></p><p>This bill eliminates the deferral of tax for shareholders who receive stock through corporate mergers, acquisitions, or transfers involving corporations with annual gross receipts exceeding $500 million over the three preceding taxable year period.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
